{"tid":132771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又一城再現「水舞間」5層水柱一地迹","createTime":"2017-02-24T05:31:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-25T02:29:34.000Z","uid":37524,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"62d7b5072564abb802fc7bca973f0af5c9d7bab3","tid":132771,"uid":37524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T05:31:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170224/56346508\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170224%2F56346508&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQsnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=d08b39bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170224%2F56346508&h=fe51e640\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170224/56346508</a><br />\n<br />\n九龍塘又一城商場於14年3月30日，因天降冰雹和持續大雨引發水災，出現全商場水浸的「水舞間」奇景(<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2mqUs1b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2mqUs1b&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQsnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=dffbc188\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2mqUs1b</a>)，今凌晨「水舞間」再度重演。<br />\n<br />\n凌晨約2時半，商場天花約4至6個消防水龍頭爆裂，噴出水柱及水花，射向走廊及地面，7層商場中多層走廊有水迹，最低層地庫受影響最嚴重出現水浸，幸而商舖未受波及。事發時消防員曾接報到場。<br />\n據稱，事發約15分鐘後，職員才關掉水掣，並且用沙包堆放扶手電梯旁，以防滲水造成故障。其後工人通宵清理走廊及地面水迹，以及用抽風機吹乾。工程人員進行緊急維修。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170224/large/1487900904_f8c7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170224%2Flarge%2F1487900904_f8c7.jpg&h=44151247&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170224/large/1487880292_5663.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170224%2Flarge%2F1487880292_5663.jpg&h=de0aec0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n商場爆水龍頭噴出水花。(黃江奇攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170224/large/1487880340_eccb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170224%2Flarge%2F1487880340_eccb.jpg&h=369d95bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n水龍頭射出水柱。(黃江奇攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170224/large/1487880361_444e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170224%2Flarge%2F1487880361_444e.jpg&h=f46b32e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n地面有水迹。(黃江奇攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170224/large/1487880418_86f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170224%2Flarge%2F1487880418_86f0.jpg&h=c2bf4b7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n工人在地庫清理積水。(黃江奇攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170224/large/1487888978_6660.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170224%2Flarge%2F1487888978_6660.jpg&h=954487fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n工人用水桶清理積水。(黃江奇攝)"},{"pid":"a7e0b25ff39c771aae9564802cdb91ad38861090","tid":132771,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T05:33:50.000Z","msg":"即刻諗起某首歌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a95935f1b12b3498fc2b0707a409344cdc28e4bb","tid":132771,"uid":39871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T05:34:08.000Z","msg":"年度商場活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a614e9a953da7d9eb22f8d5284c5174edb9220e","tid":132771,"uid":57762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T06:26:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 